user.biography: A Place Like No Other™. Home to 71 rides, including 18 roller coasters, Cedar Point Shores Waterpark and more.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 10, 2021. May be an image of nature.

node.text:
It's been a long week, and we've missed you! We'll see you tomorrow when we reopen our gates for the weekend! 

See our hours for Sept. and Oct. here: bit.ly/3dm2WEx

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 08, 2021. May be an image of 8 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text:
There's still time to apply for great fall jobs. 🎃 

Starting at $20/hour, we have openings all over the park. We need costume stitchers, performers, techs and that's just with our Live Entertainment Team!

There's something for everyone! Apply now at: cedarpoint.com/jobs

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 07, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text:
Wicked Twister wasn't the only retiree yesterday... 

From changing coaster train wheels, to reassembling the cabins on Giant Wheel each year, Frank did it all! Congratulations on nearly 40 years of service to Cedar Point! Enjoy your retirement. 😄

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 06, 2021. May be an image of 3 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: Today is TRUCE DAY at Forbidden Frontier on Adventure Island! 🎉 Visit as the residents end the season with an EPIC finale around 6:00 p.m. Drama and conflict are coming to the island... and that's jus’ the beginning! 😳😁

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 06, 2021. May be an image of outdoors and text that says 'A PASS LIKE NO OTHER 2022 GOLD PASS T Cedar Point GOLDPASS GOLD PASS 2022'.

node.text:
Only a few hours left to get a 2022 Gold Pass for ONLY $99! The price goes up at midnight! 
cedarpoint.com/pass

Read more here: bit.ly/3mX4XMj

node.text:
Tomorrow is the LAST DAY to get the lowest price of the season on the 2022 Gold Pass! 😵 
For only $99 you get: 
✅ Unlimited visits to Cedar Point
✅ Unlimited visits to Cedar Point Shores
✅ FREE parking
Get yours now: cedarpoint.com/pass

node.text:
🚨 Special Passholder Offer Alert! 🚨 
Stay two nights at Hotel Breakers 9/10-9/12 for only $299. You’ll want to cash in on this deal quickly as availability is limited and the offer ends September 6th. 

Book here: bit.ly/2kcDpVb

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 04, 2021. May be an image of outdoors and text that says 'A PASS LIKE NO OTHER 2022 GOLD PASS T Cedar Point GOLDPASS GOLD PASS 2022'.

node.text:
Going, going... the best deal on Cedar Point's Gold Pass won't last❗ 😮 

Get unlimited visits to Cedar Point and Cedar Point Shores for all of 2022 and the rest of 2021 PLUS free parking for only $99 until Monday!

Get yours now: cedarpoint.com/pass.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 04, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, child, people sitting and outdoors.

node.text:
This is the LAST WEEKEND for fun at Forbidden Frontier on Adventure Island in 2021! Be sure to play at Highground and visit the residents one last time! 😍 

On Monday, see this year's epic cliffhanger around 6:00 p.m. Conflict & drama are just the beginning of this new tale...

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 03, 2021. May be an image of 7 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text:
Spooky Season is almost here! 🎃 Join our team!
Positions available include:
🍬 Trick-or-Treat Assistance
🌭 Food & Beverage
🎢 Ride and Park Operations
👹 Scare Actors
👕 Merch & Games
We're hiring for day and night help starting at $20/hour!

Apply now: cedarpoint.com/jobs
